WEBVTT

00:00:00.834 --> 00:00:02.499
di katastrofe

00:00:02.740 --> 00:00:04.726
Khane Oyfman

00:00:05.424 --> 00:00:06.653
di tsveyte

00:00:06.689 --> 00:00:07.865
kasete.

00:00:09.676 --> 00:00:11.276
ir hot dertseylt

00:00:11.313 --> 00:00:12.438
azoy

00:00:13.827 --> 00:00:15.470
ir hot in der heym

00:00:15.470 --> 00:00:16.600
di mame

00:00:16.645 --> 00:00:17.706
gebakt

00:00:17.706 --> 00:00:18.648
gekokht

00:00:18.586 --> 00:00:19.255
DA.

00:00:18.940 --> 00:00:20.521
dertseylt vayter.

00:00:20.797 --> 00:00:22.946
di mame hot gebakn, gekokht.

00:00:22.946 --> 00:00:24.034
un

00:00:24.034 --> 00:00:26.832
 shoyn dertseyln fun der milkhome

00:00:27.462 --> 00:00:28.216
UNK

00:00:30.483 --> 00:00:31.422
farmisht.

00:00:32.035 --> 00:00:35.995
dertseylt, azoy iz bay aykh geven,

00:00:36.457 --> 00:00:38.290
in der heym

00:00:38.617 --> 00:00:41.632
ven di mame hot gebakt broyt vifl.

00:00:41.182 --> 00:00:46.728
UNK ONA PEKLA, zi hot gebakn broyt fraytik.

00:00:47.628 --> 00:00:54.288
ale fraytik hot zi gebakn broyt, opgekokht oyf shabes, me zol nit kokhn shabes.

00:00:56.049 --> 00:00:58.794
hot zi opgebakn, opgekokht.

00:00:58.985 --> 00:01:01.370
un der tate iz gekumen funem dorf

00:01:01.370 --> 00:01:05.940
er iz gan in shul arayn, zikh opgebodn, gan in shul arayn, azoy balebatish.

00:01:06.258 --> 00:01:07.830
geven ales.

00:01:08.182 --> 00:01:14.498
hot o- der tate gekumen, geven opgebakn, opgekokht, opgevashn di pol un untergeshmirt

00:01:14.498 --> 00:01:16.664
iz geven VSYO KHOROSHO.

00:01:18.307 --> 00:01:22.368
dertseylt ven hot ir gegangen in shkole?

00:01:22.947 --> 00:01:25.233
ven,? ikh bin gan in shkole arayn

00:01:25.233 --> 00:01:27.823
bin alt geven zibn yor

00:01:27.823 --> 00:01:31.713
bin ikh gan in shkole in PERVYI klas. in der yidisher shkole bin ikh gan.

00:01:31.713 --> 00:01:36.430
ale kinder zenen gan in der yidisher shkole un ikh bin gan in der yidisher shkole.

00:01:37.190 --> 00:01:42.027
⟨TAK BYLO⟩ yidishe shkole geven biz zibn klas.

00:01:42.286 --> 00:01:48.119
un, un, ah, ver s'hot gevolt iz gegan DAL'SHE in der ukraynisher shkole.

00:01:48.209 --> 00:01:51.590
nor dos zibn klas iz men ⟨UCHILOS⟩ UNK

00:01:51.590 --> 00:01:53.784
mir hobn gelernt in der yidisher

00:01:55.600 --> 00:01:57.215
in der yidisher shkole.

00:01:55.769 --> 00:01:56.499
nu

00:01:57.710 --> 00:02:00.168
ir gedenkt

00:02:00.410 --> 00:02:02.446
azoy iz geven di shkole?

00:02:02.553 --> 00:02:03.526
dertseylt.

00:02:03.380 --> 00:02:05.503
di di shkole iz geven

00:02:05.503 --> 00:02:10.023
m'hot zikh gelernt, iz geven gute UCHITELI; DIREKTOR ⟨SHKOLA⟩ a yid

00:02:10.023 --> 00:02:12.123
same yidishe UCHITELIs

00:02:11.939 --> 00:02:12.569
s-

00:02:12.123 --> 00:02:14.453
DIREKTOR SHKOLY iz geven a yid.

00:02:14.433 --> 00:02:16.705
azoy hot, azoy hot im geheysn?

00:02:14.500 --> 00:02:15.710
same yidn.

00:02:16.390 --> 00:02:17.515
Blitman.

00:02:19.867 --> 00:02:23.574
di shkole iz geven vifl ETAZHNA? dertseylt.

00:02:23.022 --> 00:02:26.409
 eyn etazh iz geven.

00:02:28.996 --> 00:02:32.571
geven PERVYI klas, VTOROI, TRETII

00:02:32.571 --> 00:02:34.424
CHETVERTIY PIATIY

00:02:34.734 --> 00:02:37.497
iz, iz geven bizn zibetn.

00:02:37.497 --> 00:02:42.677
in der fri iz gan di klenere klasn; bay tog iz gan shoyn di gresere

00:02:42.677 --> 00:02:44.448
di gresere kinder.

00:02:44.774 --> 00:02:45.697
un VSE.

00:02:47.660 --> 00:02:49.612
vos hot ir gelernt dortn?

00:02:49.989 --> 00:02:53.504
 mir hobn gelernt historye

00:02:53.549 --> 00:02:54.719
yidish

00:02:54.719 --> 00:02:56.530
geografye

00:02:59.320 --> 00:03:01.627
NEMETSK hot men gelernt.

00:03:01.936 --> 00:03:04.617
geven a UROK a rusishe.

00:03:04.617 --> 00:03:07.280
geven a UROK a ukraynishe.

00:03:07.994 --> 00:03:11.240
iz, un, a matematike geven.

00:03:11.251 --> 00:03:12.680
ales iz geven.

00:03:13.225 --> 00:03:13.962
DA.

00:03:14.997 --> 00:03:16.592
yidishe bikhlekh

00:03:16.592 --> 00:03:19.782
yidish UNK mir hobn geshribn diktantn iz geve-

00:03:19.782 --> 00:03:23.390
azoy iz geven vi me geyt itstert in shkole, azoy iz geven demolt.

00:03:23.390 --> 00:03:24.132
nor i-

00:03:24.132 --> 00:03:26.798
demolts iz geven oyf yidish

00:03:26.798 --> 00:03:28.998
un itstert iz oyf ukraynish.

00:03:32.615 --> 00:03:34.837
avelkhe nokh geven dortn shkole?

00:03:35.247 --> 00:03:37.874
geven a ukraynishe tsvey shkoles.

00:03:39.618 --> 00:03:43.966
i- ie hot geDRUZet mit di ukraynishe meydelekh, yingelekh?

00:03:43.044 --> 00:03:44.844
oykhet, DA.

00:03:44.917 --> 00:03:48.640
mir hobn geDRUZHet. UNK CHAS fleg ikh geyn mit di yidishe meydlekh.

00:03:48.950 --> 00:03:51.307
iz geven yidishe meydlekh, fleg ikh geyn.

00:03:50.604 --> 00:03:52.927
ir gedenkt mit vemen hot ir

00:03:52.679 --> 00:03:55.306
DA, mit Khave Sapozhnik.

00:03:57.337 --> 00:03:58.884
Zisl

00:04:00.408 --> 00:04:03.054
⟨biz⟩ mir zaynen geven fir PODRUGes.

00:04:03.057 --> 00:04:04.860
Khave un Zisl

00:04:04.860 --> 00:04:06.292
un Yides.

00:04:12.946 --> 00:04:16.552
yede hot zikh gehat zayn, zayne k- zayn kompanye.

00:04:19.139 --> 00:04:20.214
v-

00:04:19.375 --> 00:04:21.347
geven bay undz a kino.

00:04:21.347 --> 00:04:25.861
geven teater iz nit geven, kino iz geven, flegn mir geyn.

00:04:25.861 --> 00:04:27.667
tsunoyfnemen, mir flegn geyn

00:04:27.667 --> 00:04:28.814
a mol flegn

00:04:29.602 --> 00:04:34.257
flegn undz gebn biletn fun der shkole, flegn mir geyn, flegn undz firn

00:04:34.257 --> 00:04:35.570
in ⟨STROY⟩

00:04:35.829 --> 00:04:37.190
un

00:04:37.938 --> 00:04:43.585
un mir flegn geyn oyf a eskursye, flegn firn di UCHITELke ale kinder

00:04:44.975 --> 00:04:45.796
vuhin?

00:04:46.544 --> 00:04:48.395
vuhin? dortn in

00:04:50.830 --> 00:04:52.782
vuhi-, ikh gedenk shoyn vu.

00:04:58.779 --> 00:05:01.557
nu, ayere PODRUGes

00:05:01.630 --> 00:05:03.667
mit vos hot ir nokh

00:05:04.162 --> 00:05:05.304
farnemen

00:05:07.233 --> 00:05:09.860
vayter mit gornit hob ikh mir nit farnemen.

00:05:10.372 --> 00:05:13.963
gan in shkole arayn, un bin geven, ikh bin geven a kind.

00:05:13.963 --> 00:05:18.820
ibergelebt dem t- dem tog, danken got; ibergelebt di nakht, danken got.

00:05:18.505 --> 00:05:21.540
in shkole hot nokh genemen PIONERY

00:05:21.540 --> 00:05:22.195
⟨TAM⟩

00:05:23.062 --> 00:05:24.339
DA.

00:05:23.129 --> 00:05:24.744
ir gedenkt?

00:05:24.935 --> 00:05:26.330
ikh gedenk nit.

00:05:26.791 --> 00:05:28.945
nit fa- ⟨epes nit⟩ far mir; ikh gedenk

00:05:28.945 --> 00:05:32.545
tsi s'iz den geven yo pyonern tsi s'iz nit geven

00:05:32.545 --> 00:05:33.915
⟨se⟩ gedenk nit.

00:05:35.448 --> 00:05:38.986
vos hot ir ge- ge- in shkole

00:05:39.346 --> 00:05:42.057
az ir hot zikh banemen mit

00:05:45.522 --> 00:05:47.238
mit ale ⟨LOM TAM⟩

00:05:48.408 --> 00:05:50.126
shmates hot ir ge-

00:05:51.715 --> 00:05:52.942
papir

00:05:53.386 --> 00:05:54.438
UNK

00:05:54.438 --> 00:05:55.760
di UCHITELes hobn

00:05:55.850 --> 00:05:58.360
me- un se fleg zayn bay undz zayn a UROK

00:05:58.360 --> 00:06:00.680
a UNK UROK, flegn mir aleyn

00:06:00.680 --> 00:06:05.050
KUKLINY kleydelekh, PLATshkelekh

00:06:05.050 --> 00:06:09.482
m'hot tsugeshnitn, mir hobn ge- mit a nodl. s'iz geven aza UROK.

00:06:09.482 --> 00:06:10.644
flegn mir neyen.

00:06:12.877 --> 00:06:14.778
un ayer bruder

00:06:15.408 --> 00:06:16.803
vu hot zikh gelernt?

00:06:16.758 --> 00:06:19.160
mayn bruder oykhet gan in shkole.

00:06:19.171 --> 00:06:23.300
er iz gan in hekhern klas; ikh bin gan in klenern klas.

00:06:24.419 --> 00:06:26.034
nu, dertseylt.

00:06:25.027 --> 00:06:29.729
ven ikh bin gegan in ershtn klas iz er geven in tsveytn tsi in dritn klas.

00:06:32.030 --> 00:06:33.037
ir hot gezogt

00:06:32.857 --> 00:06:35.596
un er hot ge⟨KINTSH⟩et dem zibetn klas.

00:06:35.596 --> 00:06:39.663
iz er geforn keyn Ades, zikh lernen zayn a toker.

00:06:39.691 --> 00:06:42.041
un dernokhdem hot mayn tate gezogt

00:06:42.041 --> 00:06:47.081
az er iz shoyn a por khadoshim az er darf geyn in der armey "vos darf ikh zikh ⟨itst⟩ kinder mutshen?"

00:06:47.081 --> 00:06:48.971
hot der tate azoy gezogt.

00:06:48.971 --> 00:06:52.111
iz di mame geforn, hot im ⟨um⟩genemen

00:06:52.111 --> 00:06:55.097
un hot, m'hot im USTROYet in ⟨Ades⟩

00:06:55.097 --> 00:06:56.379
hot er gearbet.

00:06:56.379 --> 00:06:59.590
az er hot nit gevolt zitsn azoy.

00:06:59.590 --> 00:07:01.718
hot der tate im USTROYet in ⟨Ades⟩.

00:07:01.718 --> 00:07:06.073
hot er gearbet in ⟨Ades⟩ biz m'hot UNK gedarft avekgeyn in der m- in der armey.

00:07:06.073 --> 00:07:08.097
nu, iz er avekgan in der armey.

00:07:07.906 --> 00:07:08.677
ven?

00:07:08.125 --> 00:07:08.789
VSE.

00:07:08.834 --> 00:07:09.571
ha?

00:07:10.505 --> 00:07:12.575
ven iz er gegangen in der armey?

00:07:12.969 --> 00:07:14.431
far der milkhome.

00:07:15.584 --> 00:07:17.367
ir gedenkt avelekh yor?

00:07:16.681 --> 00:07:19.392
azoy dakht zikh mir dos nayn un draysikte yor.

00:07:19.820 --> 00:07:23.679
iz toyznt nayn hundert ne- ne- dos nayn un draysikte yor geven.

00:07:24.258 --> 00:07:26.277
mayn bruder avekgan in der armey.

00:07:27.734 --> 00:07:30.530
un dernokhdem gevorn di milkhome, VSE.

00:07:31.565 --> 00:07:34.495
ven iz gevor- ven iz gevorn di milkhome, gedenkt?

00:07:35.007 --> 00:07:40.927
s'hot zikh ongehoybn di milkhome in, in eyn un fertsiktn yor, tsi in fertsiktn epes azoy-o.

00:07:40.930 --> 00:07:42.143
hot zikh ongehoybn

00:07:41.015 --> 00:07:43.017
azoy hot ir, azoy

00:07:42.143 --> 00:07:44.732
⟨hot di⟩ di radyo ibergegebn.

00:07:44.732 --> 00:07:47.338
mir zaynen oyfgeshtanen "milkhome, milkhome."

00:07:47.338 --> 00:07:49.986
iz gevorn a TREVOGA, VOLNENIE.

00:07:49.986 --> 00:07:56.770
er ho- di mame hot opgeven ⟨ayngeredt⟩ fun mayn bruder, fun Arn ⟨oy⟩ vu zayne beyndelekh dort, vu, vu, vu

00:07:57.114 --> 00:08:04.516
 er hot zikh nokh ongerufn, di mame tsum tatn "⟨gut vos⟩ du host im gezen, vu er iz, vos er iz"

00:08:05.247 --> 00:08:09.455
dernokh UNK ongekumen, hot er di gantse tsayt ⟨VOYOY⟩et.

00:08:09.455 --> 00:08:12.695
un er hot UNK POPADet in keyn shum PLENNIK.

00:08:12.695 --> 00:08:15.361
er iz geven der melukhe getray, er hot ⟨VOYOY⟩et.

00:08:15.361 --> 00:08:16.497
di gantse tsayt.

00:08:16.655 --> 00:08:18.252
er hot geshraybn aykh?

00:08:18.342 --> 00:08:19.164
pruvn?

00:08:18.849 --> 00:08:21.664
 vi zhe hot er gekent undz shraybn?

00:08:21.700 --> 00:08:27.452
az er iz geven, er hot VOYOYet bay di royte, un do zenen arayngan di NEMTSes.

00:08:27.452 --> 00:08:30.128
un di RUMINTSes.

00:08:27.995 --> 00:08:30.132
nu biz der milkhome hot er geshraybn?

00:08:30.128 --> 00:08:32.565
oh, biz in der milkhome hot er undz geshribn.

00:08:32.298 --> 00:08:33.845
vos hot er geshribn?

00:08:33.749 --> 00:08:35.769
fleg undz shraybn briv.

00:08:36.888 --> 00:08:37.996
ir gedenkt

00:08:37.006 --> 00:08:39.837
a gru- fleg sh- shraybn

00:08:39.837 --> 00:08:44.893
funem tatn un fun der momen, un fleg undz ⟨POMONAY⟩en un Rivitshke's

00:08:44.893 --> 00:08:46.555
⟨POMONAY⟩en. mir hobn nit gevolt

00:08:46.555 --> 00:08:48.541
shraybn az s'hot zikh a slutshay

00:08:48.541 --> 00:08:51.119
mit Rivitshken az Rivitshke iz shoyn nishto.

00:08:51.130 --> 00:08:53.355
fleg er yeder briv shraybn.

00:08:53.355 --> 00:08:56.170
ikh kush hundert toyznt mol Rivitshke.

00:08:56.834 --> 00:09:02.080
veyst ⟨az⟩ zi iz geven a klener kind, hot zi, hot er gikher lib gehat; hot mikh oykhet libe gehat.

00:09:02.080 --> 00:09:03.379
KAK SESTRA

00:09:03.399 --> 00:09:04.273
nor di

00:09:04.273 --> 00:09:07.274
dos klenere shvesterl hot er gikher lib gehat.

00:09:09.440 --> 00:09:13.209
nu ir hot gezogt az er op- opgebn di milkhome.

00:09:13.209 --> 00:09:16.032
ir gedenkt avelekh khoydesh iz geven?

00:09:16.645 --> 00:09:18.226
di milkhome hot zikh ongehoybn?

00:09:18.114 --> 00:09:19.239
 s'nit far mir.

00:09:19.329 --> 00:09:23.373
vifl bin ikh dokh alt geven, bin farklapt der kop, ⟨hobn mir in⟩ zinen gehat.

00:09:22.923 --> 00:09:26.832
nu, dertseylt, azoy iz geven, ver iz geven bay aykh

00:09:27.294 --> 00:09:28.750
ver iz gekumen

00:09:28.750 --> 00:09:30.936
azoy hot zikh ⟨ongehoybn⟩ di milkhome?

00:09:30.145 --> 00:09:35.035
az s'hot zikh ongehoybn di milkhome, di mame iz aroysgegan, hot ⟨zi⟩ ge⟨UNK⟩ di milkhome

00:09:30.936 --> 00:09:31.996
in ayer

00:09:32.052 --> 00:09:32.806
shtot

00:09:35.035 --> 00:09:36.936
iz ge- hot di di mame

00:09:36.936 --> 00:09:39.204
zikh ongerufn tsum tatn "danken got

00:09:39.204 --> 00:09:42.457
vos du bist nit in Tambov, vos du bist khotsh in der heym"

00:09:42.498 --> 00:09:44.199
azoy hot mayn tate gezogt.

00:09:44.219 --> 00:09:46.463
hot mayn mame gezogt tsum tatn

00:09:46.463 --> 00:09:50.731
nor undzer Arn vu er iz veyst eyn got

00:09:51.509 --> 00:09:58.507
un far der milkhome hot mayn mame be- UNK dos iz di Rivitshke

00:09:58.664 --> 00:10:03.412
hobn mir nor fun mir, nor ikh bin geven, mit mayn tatn, mit mayn mamen.

00:10:03.412 --> 00:10:05.139
zenen mir ale dray geven.

00:10:05.549 --> 00:10:09.343
mir zaynen geven fir, iz dokh mayn bruder geven in der armey

00:10:09.343 --> 00:10:12.371
un dernokhdem hobn mir, hot men gevust vu er iz.

00:10:12.350 --> 00:10:16.372
nu dertseylt KAKO- ver iz geven bay aykh in Myastkivke?

00:10:16.400 --> 00:10:17.773
ver iz geven

00:10:17.773 --> 00:10:18.988
di rumenen?

00:10:18.779 --> 00:10:24.944
iz durkhgan iz bay undz durkhgan bay undz a tsentralne o-

00:10:18.988 --> 00:10:21.490
tsi di, tsi di, tsi di DEUTSCHEN

00:10:24.944 --> 00:10:30.192
i- iz durkhgegan di RUMINTSes, un s'iz durkhgegan di NEMTSes.

00:10:30.192 --> 00:10:33.522
az s'iz do geven VREDNO, m'hot zikh opgerisn

00:10:33.522 --> 00:10:37.395
iz dortn bay undz akegn a shkheyne geven finef meydlekh

00:10:37.423 --> 00:10:40.089
hot men zey ⟨NAS-⟩ NASILOVet.

00:10:40.092 --> 00:10:41.676
s'hot zikh gelozt hern.

00:10:41.676 --> 00:10:43.360
guts un shlekhts.

00:10:43.940 --> 00:10:46.364
un s'hot zikh gehert,

00:10:46.488 --> 00:10:51.918
ales ⟨hobn⟩ dernokhdem az s'hot zikh shoyn opgeshtelt heyst es der ⟨VLAST⟩, m'iz durkhgegan.

00:10:51.918 --> 00:10:55.256
iz di, iz bay undz geven di RUMINTSes.

00:10:55.314 --> 00:10:57.603
iz geven a

00:10:57.828 --> 00:10:59.875
aza min, vi azoy zogt men?

00:10:59.875 --> 00:11:02.598
shoyn fargesn vi... a zhandarmerye.

00:11:03.177 --> 00:11:07.599
⟨un mir⟩ m'hot, m'hot geru- m'hot undz gerufn oyf arbet

00:11:07.599 --> 00:11:09.923
un m'hot gegebn a PRIKAZ me zol onton

00:11:09.923 --> 00:11:13.536
heyst es a ⟨mezhe⟩ Dovid

00:11:13.572 --> 00:11:18.944
ale, un ver s'hot di yidn hobn zenen gan hot men shtrafirt.

00:11:18.944 --> 00:11:21.813
hot men geshlogn mit der nagayke

00:11:21.813 --> 00:11:24.758
di mame iz gan, ⟨hot⟩ ibergelozt mayn tatn shlaf

00:11:24.758 --> 00:11:28.378
un m'hot zi gerufn oyf der arbet, hob ikh moyre gehat tsu blaybn.

00:11:28.378 --> 00:11:33.814
hob ikh, bin ikh gan mit der mamen, di mame hot getrogn dem snop shtroy, un ikh hob getrogn

00:11:33.814 --> 00:11:35.032
mit der zerne.

00:11:35.223 --> 00:11:38.542
ikh bin gegan, der snop iz geven greser fun mir.

00:11:39.155 --> 00:11:44.566
ah! tsugegan a, di RUMINTSes, mit di nagayke mikh geshlogn.

00:11:45.365 --> 00:11:48.160
iz mayn mame tsugegan, "vos shlogstu?"

00:11:48.419 --> 00:11:53.780
⟨heyst es⟩ ikh bin nisht, ⟨akh⟩ a TRUDNE gl- yid.

00:11:54.106 --> 00:11:55.822
UNK

00:11:56.182 --> 00:11:58.432
